* Carnage landed on her feet and front limbs, the kick had bruised her ribs 
and she was sure of it.
She got to her feet and snapped at Cyber Claw as she transformed, Carnage 
shifted her weight from one leg to the other.
It was then that she heard Cyber Claw yell at her and say that somebot sent 
her, she looked back and saw Teltoli looking from behind a tree...the best 
place for her for now.
Carnage then looked at the transformer and snarled, she had no idea what the 
clone was talking about!*

" What in the Pit are you talking about?!I wasn't sent by anybot! I'm just 
trying to get my friend to the Maximal base!!!What's your problem?!"

* Carnage breathed hard, the mech fluid still running down her neck and 
dripping from her claws. Now she thought that she understood, this clone was 
running from something or somebot and it thought that she was sent to track 
it down and destroy it.
Carnage looked the bot over and sneered, even if it was supposed to be a 
female clone of Dinobot it was made very poorly, by her standards anyway.
She paced in front of the clone, ready for another attack if it decided to 
jump at her.
